  line `S ECTIONS`
  line `45 - I. Definitions.`
  line `45 - IA. Requirement of registration and net owned fund.`
  line `45 - IB. Maintenance of percentage of assets.`
  line `45 - IC. Reserve fund.`
  line `45 - ID. Power of Bank to remove directors from office.`
  line `45 - IE. Supersession of Board of directors of non - banking financial company (Other than Government`
  line `Company).`
  line `45J. Bank to regulate or prohibit issue of prospectus or advertisement soliciting deposits of money.`
  line `45JA. Power of Bank to determine policy and issue directions.`
  line `45K. Power of Bank to collect information from non - banking institutions as to deposits and to give`
  line directions.
  line `45L. Power of Bank to call for information from financial institutions and t o give directions.`
  line `45M.Duty of non - banking institutions to furnish statements, etc., required by Bank.`
  line `45MA. Powers and duties of auditors.`
  line `45MAA. Power to take action against auditors.`
  line `45MB. Power of Bank to prohibit acceptance of deposit and alienation of assets.`
  line `45MBA. Resolution of non - banking financial company.`
  line `45MC. Power of Bank to file winding up petition.`
  line `45N. Inspection.`
  line `45NA. Deposits not to be solicited by unauthorised person.`
  line `45NAA. Power in respect of group companies.`
  line `45NB. Disclosure of info rmation.`
  line `45NC. Power of Bank to exempt.`
  line `45 - O. [ Omitted. ].`
  line `45P. [ Omitted. ].`
  line `45Q. Chapter IIIB to override other laws.`
  line `45QA. Power of Company Law Board to offer repayment of deposit.`
  line `45QB. Nomination by depositors.`
  line `CHAPTER IIIC`
  line `P ROHINITION OF ACCEPTANCE OF DEPOSITS BY UNINCORPORATED BODIES`
  line `45R. Interpretation.`
  line `45S. Deposits not to be accepted in certain cases.`
  line `45T. Power to issue search warrants.`
  line `CHAPTER IIID`
  line `R EGULATION OF TRANSACTIONS IN DERIVATIVES, MONEY MARKET INSTRUMENTS,`
  line `SECURITIES, ETC.`
  line `45U. Definitions.`
