  line `S ECTIONS`
  line `45V. Transactions in derivatives.`
  line `45W. Power to regulate transactions in derivatives, money market instruments, etc.`
  line `45X. Duty to comply with directions and furnish information.`
  line `CHAPTER IIIE`
  line `J OINT M ECHANISM`
  line `45Y. Joint Mechanism.`
  line `CHAPTER IIIF`
  line `M ONETARY P OLICY`
  line `45Z. Provisions of this Chapter to override other provisions of Act.`
  line `45ZA. Inflation target.`
  line `45ZB. Constitution of Monetary Policy Committee.`
  line `45ZC. Eligibility and selection of Members appointed by Central Government.`
  line `45ZD. Terms and conditions of appointment of Members of Monetary Policy Committee.`
  line `45ZE. Removal of Members of Monetary Policy Committee.`
  line `45ZF. Vacancies, etc., not to invalidate proceedings of Monetary Policy Committee.`
  line `45ZG. Secretary to Monetary Policy Commit tee.`
  line `45ZH. Information for Monetary Policy Committee Members.`
  line `45Z - I. Meetings of Monetary Policy Committee.`
  line `45ZJ. Steps to be taken to implement decision of Monetary Policy Committee.`
  line `45ZK. Publication of decisions.`
  line `45ZL. Publication of proceedings of meet ing of Monetary Policy Committee.`
  line `45ZM. Monetary Policy Report.`
  line `45ZN. Failure to maintain inflation target.`
  line `45ZO. Power to make rules.`
  line `CHAPTER IV`
  line `G ENERAL PROVISION S`
  line `46. Contribution by Central Government to the Reserve Fund.`
  line `46A. Contribution to National Rural Credit (Long Term Operations) Fund and National Rural Credit`
  line `(Stabilisation) Fund.`
  line `46C. National Industrial Credit (Long Term Operations) Fund.`
  line `46D. National Housing Credit (Long Term Operations) Fund.`
  line `47. Allocation of surplus profits.`
  line `48. Exemption of Banks from income - tax and super - tax.`
  line `49. Publication of Bank rate.`
  line `50. Auditors.`
  line `51. Appointment of special auditors by Government.`
