obj_root_law_sections_7_content:
  string
  line 7
  line `1 * * * * *`
  line `2 [( bva ) “ Consumer Price Index ” means the Consumer Price Index Combined published by the`
  line `Government of India from time to time;]`
  line `3 [ 4 [( bvi )] “ Deposit Insurance Corporation ” means the Deposit Insurance Corporation established`
  line `under section 3 of the Deposit Insurance Corporation Act, 1961 (47 of 1961);]`
  line `5 * * * * *`
  line `6 * * * * *`
  line `7 [( bviiia ) “ Exim Bank ” means the Export - Import Bank of India established under the Export -`
  line `Import Bank of India Act, 1981 (28 of 1981);]`
  line `8 [( bix ) “ foreign currency ” and “ foreign exchange ” have the meanings respectively assigned to`
  line `them in the Foreign Exchange Regulation Act, 1973 (46 of 1973);`
  line `( c ) “ Industrial Finance Corporation ” means the Industrial Finance Corporation of India`
  line `established under the Industrial Finance Corporation Act, 1948 (15 of 1948);]`
  line `2 [( ci ) “ inflation ” means the year wise change in monthly Consumer Price Index expressed in`
  line `terms of percentage;`
  line `( cii ) “ inflation target ” means the inflation target determined in accordance with sub - section ( 1 ) of`
  line `section 45ZA;]`
  line `9 [( ca ) “ International Development Association ” means the “ Association ” referred to in the`
  line `International Development Association (Status, Immunities and Privileges) Act, 1960 (32 of 1960);`
  line `( cb ) “ International Finance Corporation ” means the “ Corporation ” referred to in the International`
  line `Finance Corporat ion (Status, Immunities and Privileges) Act, 1958 (42 of 1958);`
  line `( cc ) “ International Monetary Fund ” and “ International Bank for Reconstruction`
  line `andDevelopment" means respectively the “ International Fund ” and the “ International Bank ”, referred`
  line `to in the International Monetary Fund and Bank Act, 1945;]`
  line `2 [( cci ) “ Monetary Policy Committee ” means the Committee constituted under sub - section ( 1 ) of`
  line `section 45ZB;]`
  line `10 [ ccc ) “ National Bank ” means the National Bank for Agriculture and Rural Development`
  line `established un der section 3 of the National Bank for Agriculture and Rural Development Act, 1981`
  line `(61 of 1981);]`
  line `11 [( ccci ) “National Bank for Financing Infrastructure and Development” means the Institution`
  line `established under section 3 of the National Bank for Financing Inf rastructure and Development Act,`
  line 2021;
  line `( cccii ) “other development financial institution” means a development financial institution`
  line `licensed under section 29 of the National Bank for Financing Infrastructure and Development Act,`
  line 2021;]
  line `12 [( cccc ) “ National Housing Bank ” means the National Housing Bank established under`
  line `section 3 of the National Housing Bank Act, 1987 (53 of 1987);]`
  line `2 [( cccci ) “ Policy Rate ” means the rate for repo - transactions under sub - section ( 12AB ) of section 17;]`
  line `13 * * * * *`
  line `1. Clauses ( bi ), ( bii ), ( biii ), ( biv ) and ( bv ) omitted by Act 61 of 1981, s. 61 and the Second Schedule (w.e.f. 12 - 7 - 1982). Earlier`
  line `these clauses were substituted by Act 23 of 1965, s. 2, for clause ( bb ) (w.e.f. 1 - 3 - 1966).`
  line `2. Ins. by Act 28 of 2016, s. 221 (w.e.f. 27 - 6 - 2016).`
  line `3. Ins. by Act 47 of 1961, s. 2 and the Second Schedule (w.e.f. 1 - 1 - 1962).`
  line `4. Clause ( bbb ) re - lettered as clause ( bvi ) thereof by Act 23 of 1965, s. 2 (w.e.f. 1 - 3 - 1966).`
  line `5. Clause ( bvii ) omitted by Act 53 of 2003, s. 12 and the Schedule (w.e.f. 2 - 7 - 2004).`
  line `6. Clause ( bviii ) omi tted by Act 61 of 1981, s. 61 and the Second Schedule (w.e.f. 12 - 7 - 1982).`
  line `7. Ins. by Act 28 of 1981, s. 40 and the Second Schedule (w.e.f. 1 - 1 - 1982).`
  line `8. Subs. by Act 24 of 1978, s. 3, for clause ( c ) (w.e.f. 21 - 7 - 1978).`
  line `9. Ins. by Act 51 of 1974, s. 2 (w.e. f. 13 - 12 - 1974).`
  line `10. Ins. by Act 61 of 1981, s. 61 and the Second Schedule (w.e.f. 12 - 7 - 1982).`
  line `11. Ins. by Act 17 of 2021, s. 47 and the S econd Schedule (w.e.f. 19 - 4 - 2021).`
