obj_root_law_sections_8_content:
  string
  line 8
  line `1 [( cv ) “ Reconstruction Bank ” means the Industrial Reconstruction Bank of India established`
  line `under section 3 of the Industrial Reconstruction Bank of India Act, 1984 (62 of 1984);]`
  line `( d ) “ rupee coin ” means 2 *** rupees which are legal tender 3 [in 4 [India]] und er the provisions of`
  line `the Indian Coinage Act, 1906 (3 of 1906); 5 ***`
  line `( e ) “ scheduled bank ” means a bank included in the Second Schedule;`
  line `6 [( el ) “ Small Industries Bank ” means the Small Industries Development Bank of India established`
  line `under section 3 of the Small Industries Development Bank of India Act, 1989 (39 of 1989); ]`
  line `7 [( ea ) “ Sponsor Bank ” means a Sponsor Bank as defined in the Regional Rural Banks Act, 1976`
  line `(21 of 1976);]`
  line `8 [ 9 [( eb )] “ State Bank ” means the State Bank of India constituted under the State Bank of India`
  line `Act, 1955 (23 of 1955);]`
  line `10 * * * * *`
  line `11 [( fi ) “ State Financial Corporation ” means any State Financial Corporation established under the`
  line `State Financial Corporations Act, 1951 (63 of 1951);]`
  line `12 * * * * *`
  line `13 [( g ) “ Unit Trust ” means the Unit Trust of India established under section 3 of the Unit Trust of`
  line `India Act, 1963 (52 of 19 63);]`
  line `14 [( h ) “ agricultural operations ”, “ central co - operative bank ”, “ co - operative society ”, “ crops ”,`
  line `“ marketing of corps ”, “ pisciculture ”, “ regional rural bank ” and “ State co - operative bank ” shall have`
  line `the meanings respectively assigned to them in the National Bank for Agriculture and Rural`
  line `Development Act, 1981 (61 of 1981);`
  line `( i ) “ co - operative bank ”, “ co - operative credit society ”, “ director ”, “ primary agricultural credit`
  line `society ”, “ primary co - operative bank ” and “ primary credit society ” shall have the meanings`
  line `respectively assigned to them in Part V of the Banking Regulation Act, 1949 (10 of 1949).]`
  line `CHAPTER II`
  line `I NCORPORATION, 15 [CAPITAL], MANAGEMENT AND BUSINESS`
  line `3. Establishment and incorporation of Reserve Bank. — ( 1 ) A bank to be called the Reserve Bank`
  line `of India shall be constituted for the purposes of taking over the management of the currency from the`
  line `16 [Central Government] and of carrying on the business of bankin g in accordance with the provisions of`
  line `this Act.`
  line `( 2 ) The Bank shall be a body corporate by the name of the Reserve Bank of India, having perpetual`
  line `succession and a common seal, and shall by the said name sue and be sued.`
  line `1. Ins. by Act 62 of 1984, s. 71 and the Third Schedule (w.e.f. 20 - 3 - 1985).`
  line `2. The word “silver” omitted by Act 62 of 1948, s. 7 and the Schedule (w.e.f. 1 - 1 - 1949).`
  line `3. Ins. by the M.O. 1937.`
  line `4. Subs. by Act 32 of 1951, s. 2, for “the States” (w.e.f. 1 - 11 - 1951).`
  line `5. The word “and” omitted by the M.O. 1937.`
  line `6. Ins. by Act 39 of 1989, s. 53 and the Second Schedule (w.e.f. 7 - 3 - 1990).`
  line `7. Ins. by Act 21 of 1976, s. 33 (w.e.f. 26 - 9 - 1975).`
  line `8. Ins. by Act 23 of 1955, s. 52 and the Third Schedule (w.e.f. 1 - 7 - 1955). Earlier clause ( ee ) inserted by the A.O. 1950 which was`
  line `later omitted by Act 32 of 1951, s. 4 (w.e.f. 1 - 11 - 1951).`
  line `9. Clause ( ee ) re - let tered as clause ( eb ) thereof by Act 21 of 1976, s. 33 (w.e.f. 26 - 9 - 1975).`
  line `10. Clause ( f ) omitted by Act 61 of 1981, s. 61 and the Second Schedule (w.e.f. 12 - 7 - 1982).`
  line `11. Ins. by Act 24 of 1978, s. 3 (w.e.f. 21 - 7 - 1978).`
  line `12. Clauses ( f ) to ( k ) omitted by Act 11 of 1947, s. 2 (w.e.f. 1 - 4 - 1947) which was earlier inserted by the M.O. 1937.`
  line `13. Ins. by Act 52 of 1963, s. 44 and the Second Schedule (w.e.f. 1 - 2 - 1964). Earlier clause ( g ) was inserted by Act 32 of 1951,`
  line `s. 4 (w.e.f. 1 - 11 - 1951) which was lat er omitted by Act 62 of 1956, s. 2 and the Schedule (w.e.f. 1 - 11 - 1956).`
  line `14. Ins. by Act 61 of 1981, s. 61 and the Second Schedule (w.e.f. 12 - 7 - 1982).`
  line `15. Subs. by Act 62 of 1948, s. 7 and the Schedule, for “SHARE CAPITAL” (w.e.f. 1 - 1 - 1949).`
  line `16. Subs. by th e M.O. 1937, for “G.G. in C.”.`
