obj_root_law_sections_14_content:
  string
  line 14
  line `1 [( b ) the purchase sale and rediscount of bills of exchange (including treasury bills) drawn in or`
  line `on any place in any country outside India which is a member of the International Monetary Fund and`
  line `maturing, —`
  line `( i ) in the case of bills of exchange arising out of any bona fide transaction relating to the`
  line `export of goods from India, within one hundred and eighty days, and`
  line `( ii ) in any other case, within ninety days,`
  line `from the date of such purchase or rediscount:`
  line `Provid ed that no such purchase, sale or rediscount shall be made in India except with a`
  line `scheduled bank or a State co - operativ e bank;]`
  line `2 * * * * *`
  line `3 [( 3A ) the making to any scheduled bank or State co - operative bank, or loans and advances,`
  line `against promissory notes or such bank, repayable on demand or on the expiry of fixed periods not`
  line `exceeding one hundred and eighty days:`
  line `Provided that the borrowing bank furnishes a declaration in writing, to the effect that —`
  line `( i ) it holds bills of exchange arising out of any transaction relating to the export of goods`
  line `from India of a value not less than the am ount of such loans or advances, —`
  line `( a ) drawn in India and no any place in any country outside India which is a member of`
  line `the International Monetary Fund or in any other country notified in this behalf by the Bank in`
  line `the Gazette of India, and`
  line `4 [( b ) maturing not later than one hundred and eighty days from the date of the loan or`
  line `advance, and it will, so long as any part of such loans and advances remains unpaid, continue`
  line `to hold such bills of exchange of a value not less than the amount of such loans or advances`
  line `outstanding for the time being; or]`
  line `5 [( ii ) it has granted a pre - shipment loan or advance to an exporter or any other person in India`
  line `in order to enable him to export goods from India, the amount of the loan or advance drawn and`
  line `outstanding at any time being not less than the outstanding amount of the loan or advance`
  line `obtained by the borrowing bank from the Bank.]]`
  line `6 [( 3B ) the making to any scheduled bank or State co - operative bank or loans and advances`
  line `repayable on demand or on the expiry of fixed periods not exceeding one hundred and eighty days`
  line `against promissory notes of such bank:`
  line `Provided that the borrowing bank furnishe s a declaration in writin g to the effect that it has made`
  line `loans and advances for bona fide commercial or trade transactions or for financing agricultural`
  line `operations or the marketing of crops or for other agricultural purposes as set out in the declaration and`
  line `the said declaration includes such other particulars as may be required by the Bank;]`
  line `( 4 ) the making to 7 *** local authorities, scheduled banks 8 [, 9 *** 10 [State] co - operative`
  line `banks 11 [an d State Financial Corporations 12 ***]] or loans and advances, repayable on demand or on`
  line `the expiry of fixed periods not exceeding ninet y days, against the security of —`
  line `1. Subs. by Act 35 of 1962, s. 3, for su b - clause ( b ) (w.e.f. 15 - 9 - 1962).`
  line `2. Sub - clause ( c ) omitted by Act 62 of 1948, s. 7 and the Schedule (w.e.f. 1 - 1 - 1949).`
  line `3. Ins. by Act 35 of 1962, s. 3 (w.e.f. 15 - 9 - 1962).`
  line `4. Subs. by Act 58 of 1968, s. 24, for sub - clause ( b ) (w.e.f. 1 - 2 - 1969).`
  line `5. Subs. by s. 24, ibid., for clause ( ii ) (w.e.f. 1 - 2 - 1969).`
  line `6. Ins. by Act 51 of 1974, s. 6 (w.e.f. 13 - 12 - 1974).`
  line `7. The words and letter “Part B States” omitted by Act 32 of 1951, s. 7 (w.e.f. 1 - 11 - 1951).`
  line `8. Subs. by the M.O. 1937, for “and Provincial co - ope rative banks”.`
  line `9. The words “Burma scheduled banks” omitted by Act 11 of 1947, s. 11 (w.e.f 1 - 4 - 1947).`
  line `10. Subs. by the A.O. 1950, for “Provincial”.`
  line `11. Subs. by Act 19 of 1957, s. 2, for certain words (w.e.f. 8 - 6 - 1957).`
  line `12. The words and figures “establis hed under the State Financial Corporations Act, 1951” omitted by Act 24 of 1978,`
  line `s. 4 (w.e.f. 21 - 7 - 1978).`
