obj_root_law_sections_16_content:
  string
  line 16
  line `( b ) repayable on the expiry of fixed periods not exceeding eighteen months from the date of`
  line `such loan or advance, against securities of the Central Government of any maturity or against`
  line `bonds and debentures issued by the Corporation and guaranteed by the Central Government and`
  line `maturity within a period not exceeding eighteen months from the date of such loan or advance;`
  line `1 * * * * *]`
  line `2 [( 4BB ) the making to any financial institution notified by the Central Government in this behalf,`
  line `of loans and advances, —`
  line `( a ) repayable on demand or on the expiry of fixed periods not exceeding ninety days from the`
  line `date of such loan or advance, against the securities of the Central Government or of any State`
  line `Gover nment, or`
  line `( b ) repayable on the expiry of fixed periods not exceeding eighteen months from the date of`
  line `such loan or advance, against securities of the Central Government or of any State Government,`
  line `of any maturity, or against bonds and debentures issued by that financial institution and`
  line `guaranteed by the Central Government or any State Government, and maturing within a period`
  line `not exceeding eighteen months from the date of such loan or advance:`
  line `Provided that the amount of loans and advances granted to a finan cial institution under sub -`
  line `clause ( b ) shall not, at any time, exceed in the aggregate sixty per cent. of the paid - up share capital`
  line thereof;]
  line `3 [( 4BBB ) the making to the U nit Trust of loans and advances —`
  line `( i ) repayable on demand or on the expiry of a fixed period not exceeding ninety days from the`
  line `date of such loan or advance against the security of stocks, funds and securities (other than`
  line `immovable property) in which a trustee is authorised to invest trust m oney by any law for the`
  line `tim e being in force in India; 4 ***`
  line `( ii ) repayable on demand or within a period of eighteen months from the date of such loan or`
  line `advance against the security of the bonds of the Unit Trust issued with the approval of and`
  line `guaranteed b y the Central Government;]`
  line `5 [( iii ) for the purpose of any scheme other than the first unit scheme under the Unit Trust of`
  line `India Act, 1963 (52 of 1963) on such terms and conditions and against the security of such other`
  line `property of the Unit Trust as may be specified in this behalf by the Bank;]`
  line `6 [( 4C ) the making to a Warehousing Corporation established under the Agricultural Produce`
  line `(Development and Warehousing) Corporations Act, 1956 (28 of 1956) of loans and advances, —`
  line `( a ) repayable on demand or on the exp iry of fixed periods not exceeding ninety days, from`
  line `the date of such loan or advance, against securities of the Central Government or of any State`
  line `Government, or`
  line `( b ) repayable on the expiry of fixed periods not exceeding eighteen months from the date of`
  line `s uch loan or advance, against securities of the Central Government or of any State Government,`
  line `of any maturity, or against bonds and debentures issued by the corporation to which the loan or`
  line `advance is made, and guaranteed by the Central or a State Governme nt, and maturing within a`
  line `period not exceeding eighteen months from the date of such loan or advance:`
  line `Provided that the amount of loans and advances granted under clause ( b ) shall not at any time`
  line `exceed, in the aggregate, three crores of rupees in the case of the Central Warehousing`
  line `Corporation and fifty lakhs of rupees in the case of a State Warehousing Corporation;]`
  line `1. The proviso omitted by Act 66 of 1988, s. 5 (w.e.f. 30 - 12 - 1988).`
  line `2. Subs. by Act 14 of 1960, s. 2, for clause ( 4BB ) (w.e.f. 30 - 4 - 1960). Earlier inserted by Act 19 of 1957, s. 2 (w.e.f. 8 - 6 - 1957).`
  line `3. Ins. by Act 52 of 1963, s. 44 and the Second Schedule (w.e.f. 1 - 2 - 1964).`
  line `4. The word “or” omitted by Act 17 of 1966, s. 11 (w.e.f. 10 - 6 - 1966).`
  line `5. Ins. by s. 11, ibid. (w.e.f. 10 - 6 - 1966).`
  line `6. Ins. by Act 28 of 1956, s. 55 (w.e.f. 1 - 8 - 1956).`
