obj_root_law_sections_17_content:
  string
  line 17
  line `1 [( 4D ) the making to the Deposit Insurance Corporation of loans and advances; and generally`
  line `assisting the Corporation in such manner and on s uch terms as may be determined by the Central`
  line Board;]
  line `2 [( 4DD ) the making to the National Housing Bank of loans and advances arid generally assisting`
  line `the National Housing Bank in such manner and on such terms as may be determined by the Central`
  line Board;]
  line `3 [( 4E ) the making to the National Bank of loans and advances repayable on demand or on the`
  line `expiry of fixed period not exceeding eighteen months from the date of making of the loan or advance,`
  line `either —`
  line `( i ) against the security of stocks, funds and securities (other than immovable property) in`
  line `which a trustee is authorised to invest trust money by any law for the time being in force in India;`
  line or
  line `( ii ) on such other terms and conditions as the Bank may specif y;]`
  line `4 [( 4F ) contributing to the initial Capital of the Unit Trust;]`
  line `5 [( 4G ) the making of loans and advances to, and the purchasi ng of bonds and debentures`
  line `of, 6 *** 7 [the Exim Bank] 8 [or the Reconstruction Bank] 9 [or the Small Industries Bank 10 [ or the`
  line `National Bank for Financing Infrastructure and Development or other development financial`
  line `institution] ] out of the National Industrial Credit (Long Term Operations) Fund established under`
  line `section 46C;]`
  line `2 [( 4GG ) the making of loans and advances to, and the p urchasing of bonds and debentures of, the`
  line `National Housing Bank out of the National Housing Credit (Long Term Operations) Fund established`
  line `under section 46D;]`
  line `( 4H ) the making to 6 *** 9 [ or the Small Industr ies Bank] of loans and advances —`
  line `( a ) repayable on demand or on the expiry of fixed periods not exceeding ninety days from the`
  line `date of such loan or advance against the security of stocks, funds and securities (other than`
  line `immovable property) in which a trustee is authorised to invest trust mo ney by any law for the`
  line `time being in force in India; or`
  line `( b ) against the security of bills of exchange or promissory notes, arising out of bona fide`
  line `commercial or trade transactions bearing two or more good signatures and maturing within five`
  line `years from the date of such loan or advance;]`
  line `11 [( 4 - I ) the making to scheduled banks, 12 *** 7 [the Exim Bank] 13 [the Reconstruction Bank or the`
  line `Small Industries Bank] the Industrial Finance Corporation 10 [ the National Bank for Financing`
  line `Infrastructure and Development or other development financial institution ] and any other financial`
  line `institution as may, on the recommendation of the Bank, be approved in this behalf by the Central`
  line `Government of loans and advances repayable on demand or otherwise and against such security an d`
  line `on such other terms and conditions as may be approved in this behalf by the Central Board for the`
  line `purpose of enabling such banks, or financial institution, as the case may be, to purchase foreign`
  line `exchange from the Bank for the purpose of financing the im port of capital goods or for such other`
  line `purposes as may be approved by the Central Government;]`
  line `7 [( 4J ) the making to the Exim Bank of loans and advances —`
  line `1. Ins. by Act 47 of 1961, s. 51 and the Second Schedule (w.e.f. 1 - 1 - 1962).`
  line `2. Ins. by Act 53 of 1987, s. 56 and the Second Schedule (w.e.f. 9 - 7 - 1988).`
  line `3. Subs. by Act 61 of 1981, s. 61 and the Second Schedule, for clause ( 4E ) (w.e.f. 12 - 7 - 1982).`
  line `4. Ins. by Ac 52 of 1963, s. 44 and the Second Schedule (w.e.f. 1 - 2 - 1964).`
  line `5. Ins. by Act 18 of 1964, s. 38 and the Second Schedule (w.e.f. 1 - 7 - 1964).`
  line `6. The words “the Development Bank or” omitted by Act 53 of 2003, s. 12 and the Schedule (w.e.f. 2 - 7 - 2004).`
  line `7. Ins. by Act 28 of 1981, s. 40 and the Second Schedule (w.e.f. 1 - 1 - 1982).`
  line `8. Ins. by Act 62 of 1984, s. 71 and the Third Schedule (w.e.f. 20 - 3 - 1985).`
  line `9. Ins. by Act 39 of 1989, s. 53 and the Second Schedule (w.e.f. 7 - 3 - 1990).`
  line `10. Ins. by Act 17 of 2021, s. 47 and the second Sched ule (w.e.f. 19 - 4 - 2021).`
  line `1 1. Ins. by Act 24 of 1978, s. 4 (w.e.f. 21 - 7 - 1978).`
  line `1 2. The words “the Development Bank” omitted by Act 53 of 2003, s. 12 and the Schedule (w.e.f. 2 - 7 - 2004).`
  line `1 3. Subs. by Act 39 of 1989, s. 53 and the Second Schedule, for “or the Reconstruction Bank” (w.e.f. 7 - 3 - 1990).`
