obj_root_law_sections_19_content:
  string
  line 19
  line `( 8 ) the pu rchase and sale of securities 1 [ of the Central 2 [Government or a 3 [State] Government]]`
  line `of any maturity or of such securities of a local authority 4 *** as may be specified in this behalf by`
  line `the 5 [Central Government] on the recommendation of the Central Board:`
  line `Provided that securities fully guaranteed as to principal and interest by 6 [any such`
  line `Government 7 [or authority]] shall be deemed for the purposes of this clause to be securities of such`
  line `Government 7 [or authority];`
  line `8 * * * * *`
  line `9 [( 8A ) the purchase and sale of sha res in, or the capital of 10 [the 11 [National Bank],] 12 [ the Deposit`
  line `Insurance Corporation], 13 ***, the State Bank 14 [or any other bank 15 [or financial institution] notified`
  line `by the Central Government in this behalf];]`
  line `16 [( 8AA ) the promoting, establishing, supporting or aiding in the promotion, establishment and`
  line `support of any financial institution, whether as its subsidiary or otherwise;]`
  line `17 [( 8B ) the keeping of deposits with the State Bank for such specific purposes as may be approved`
  line `by the Central Government in this behalf;]`
  line `( 9 ) the custody of monies, securities and other articles of va lue, and the collection of the`
  line `proceeds, whether principal, interest or dividends, of any such securities;`
  line `( 10 ) the sale realisation of all property, whether movable or immovable, which may in any way`
  line `come into the possession of the Bank in satisfaction, o r part satisfaction, of any of its claims;`
  line `( 11 ) the acting as agent for 18 *** the 5 [Central Government] 19 [or any 3 [State] Government 20 ***`
  line `or any local authority 21 *** ] 22 [or the Industria l Finance Corporation of India 23 ***] 24 [or any other`
  line `body corporate which is established or constituted by or under any other law] 25 [or the Government of`
  line `any such country outside India or 26 [any such person or authority] a s may be approved in this behalf`
  line `by the Central Government] in the transaction of any of the follo wing kinds of business, namely: —`
  line `( a ) the purchase and sale of gold or silver 27 [or foreign exchange];`
  line `( b ) the purchase, sale, transfer and custody of bills of exchange, securities or shares in any`
  line company;
  line `1. Subs. by the M.O. 1937, for “of the G. of I or of a L.G.”.`
  line `2. Subs. by Act 11 of 1947, s. 11, for “Government, a Provincial Government or the Government of Burma” (w.e.f. 1 - 4 - 197).`
  line `3. Subs. by the A.O. 1950, for “Provincial”.`
  line `4. The words and letter “or such Part B States” omitted by Act 32 of 1951, s. 7 (w.e.f. 1 - 11 - 1951).`
  line `5. Subs. by the M.O. 1937, for “G.G. in C.”.`
  line `6. Subs., ibid., for “the G. of I., a L.G., a local authority or State in India”.`
  line `7. Subs. by Act 32 of 1951, s. 7, for “authority or State” (w.e.f. 1 - 11 - 1951).`
  line `8. The second proviso omitted by s. 7, ibid. (w.e.f. 1 - 11 - 1951).`
  line `9. Ins. by Act 23 of 1955, s. 52 and the Third Schedule (w.e.f. 1 - 7 - 1955).`
  line `10. Ins. by Act 10 of 1963, s. 47 and the Second Schedule (w.e.f. 1 - 5 - 1963).`
  line `11. Subs. by Act 61 of 1981, s. 61 and the Second Schedule, for “Agricultural Refinance and Development Corporation”`
  line `(w.e.f. 12 - 7 - 1982).`
  line `12. Ins. by Act 47 of 1961, s. 51 and the Second Schedule (w.e.f. 1 - 1 - 1962).`
  line `13. The words “the Development Bank” omitted by Act 53 of 2003, s. 1 2 and the Schedule (w.e.f. 2 - 7 - 2004).`
  line `14. Subs. by Act 79 of 1956, s. 43 and the Second Schedule, for “or any of its subsidiary banks” (w.e.f. 22 - 10 - 1956).`
  line `15. Ins. by Act 19 of 1957, s. 2 (w.e.f. 8 - 6 - 1957).`
  line `16. Ins. by Act 53 of 1987, s. 56 and the Second Schedule (w.e.f. 9 - 7 - 1988).`
  line `17. Ins. by Act 38 of 1959, s. 64 and the Third Schedule (w.e.f. 10 - 9 - 1959).`
  line `18. The words “the Secretary of State” omitted by the A.O. 1948.`
  line `19. Subs., ibid., for certain words.`
  line `20. The words “or the Government of Burma” omit ted by Act 11 of 1947, s. 11 (w.e.f. 1 - 4 - 1947).`
  line `21. The words and letter “or any Part B State” omitted by Act 32 of 1951, s. 7 (w.e.f. 1 - 11 - 1951).`
  line `22. Ins. by Act 44 of 1949, s. 2.`
  line `23. The words “established under the Industrial Finance Corporation Act, 19 48 (15 of 1948)” omitted by Act 24 of 1978,`
  line `s. 4 (w.e.f. 21 - 7 - 1978).`
  line `24. Ins. by Act 51 of 1974, s. 6 (w.e.f. 13 - 12 - 1974).`
  line `25. Ins. by Act 32 of 1951, s. 7 (w.e.f. 1 - 11 - 1951).`
  line `26. Subs. by Act 51 of 1974, s. 6, for “any such person” (w.e.f. 13 - 12 - 1974).`
  line `27. Added by Act 23 of 1947, s. 3 (w.e.f. 18 - 4 - 1947).`
