obj_root_law_sections_20_content:
  string
  line 20
  line `( c ) the collection of the proceeds, whether principal, interest or dividends, of any securities or`
  line shares;
  line `( d ) the remittance of such proceeds, at the risk of the principal, by bills of exchange payable`
  line `either in India or elsewhere;`
  line `( e ) the management of public debt;`
  line `1 [( f ) 2 *** the issue and management of 3 *** bonds and debentures;]`
  line `4 [( 11A ) the acting as ag ent for the Central Government, —`
  line `5 [ ( a ) in guaranteeing the due performance by any small - scale industrial concern, approved by`
  line `the Central Government, of its obligations to any bank or other financial institut ion in respect of`
  line `loans and advances made, or other credit facilities provided, to it by such bank or other financial`
  line `institution and the making as such agent of payments in connection with such guarantee, and ]`
  line `( b ) in administering any scheme for subsidisi ng the rate of interest or other charges in relation`
  line `to any loans or advances made, or other credit facilities provided, by banks or other financial`
  line `institutions for the purpose of financing or facilitating any export from India and the making as`
  line `such agen t of payments on behalf of the Central Government;]`
  line `6 [( 12 ) the purchase and sale of gold or silver coins and gold and silver bullion and foreign`
  line `exchange and the opening of a gold account with the principal currency authority of any foreign`
  line `country or the Bank for International Settlements or any international or regional bank or financial`
  line `institution formed by such principal currency authority or authorities or by the Government of any`
  line `foreign country;]`
  line `7 [( 12A ) the purchase and sale of securities issued by the Government of any country outside India`
  line `or by any institution or body corporate established outside India and expressed to be payable in a`
  line `foreign currency or any international or composite currency unit, being in the case of purchase by the`
  line `Bank secu rities maturing within a period of ten years from the date of purchase:`
  line `Provided that in the case of securities of an institution or body corporate, the repayment of`
  line `principal and payment of interest in respect of such securities shall be guaranteed by the Government`
  line `of the country concerned;]`
  line `8 [( 12AA ) lending or borrowing of securities of the Central Government or a State Government or`
  line `of such securities of a local authority as may be specified in this behalf by the Central Government or`
  line `foreign securities;`
  line `( 12AB ) dealing in repo or reverse repo:`
  line `Provided that lending or borrowing of funds by way of repo or reverse repo shall not be subject to`
  line `any limitation contained in this section.`
  line `Explanation. — For the purposes of this clause, —`
  line `( a ) “ repo ” means an instrument for borrowing funds by selling securities of the Central`
  line `Government or a State Government or of such securities of a local authority as may be specified`
  line `in this behalf by the Central Government or foreign securities, with an agreement to repurchase`
  line `the said securities on a mutually agreed future date at an agreed price which includes interest for`
  line `the funds borrowed;`
  line `1. Ins. by Act 44 of 1949, s. 2.`
  line `2. The words “in respect of the aforesaid Corporation” omitted by Act 51 of 1974, s. 6 (w.e.f. 13 - 12 - 1974).`
  line `3. The word “its” omitted by s. 6, ibid. (w. e.f. 13 - 12 - 1974).`
  line `4. Subs. by Act 58 of 1968, s. 24, for clause ( 11A ) (w.e.f. 1 - 2 - 1969). Earlier it was inserted by Act 14 of 1960, s. 2`
  line `(w.e.f. 30 - 4 - 1960).`
  line `5. Restored by Act 81 of 1985, s. 12 (w.e.f. 1 - 5 - 1986). Earlier sub - clause ( a ) omitted by Act 21 of 1978, s. 9 (date to be notified).`
  line `6. Subs. by Act 24 of 1978, s. 4, for clause ( 12 ) (w.e.f. 21 - 7 - 1978).`
  line `7. Subs. by s. 4, ibid., for clause ( 12A ) (w.e.f. 21 - 7 - 1978).`
  line `8. Ins. by Act 26 of 2006, s. 2 (w.e.f. 9 - 1 - 2007).`
