obj_root_law_sections_22_content:
  string
  line 22
  line `Provided further that the total amount of such bo rrowings from persons in India 1 *** shall not at`
  line `any time exceed the amount of the 2 [capital] of the Bank;`
  line `3 * * * * *`
  line `( 15 ) the making and issue of bank notes subject to the provisions of this Act 4 ***; 5 ***`
  line `6 [( 15A ) the exercise of powers and functions and the performance of duties entrusted to the Bank`
  line `under this Act or under any other law for the time being in force;]`
  line `7 [ 15B ) the providing of facilities for training in banking and for the promotion of research, where,`
  line `in the opinion of the Bank, such provision may facilitate the exercise by the Bank of its powers and`
  line `functions, or the discharge of its duties;]`
  line `( 16 ) generally, the doing of all such matters and things as may be incidental to or consequential`
  line `upon the exercise of its powers or the discharge of its duties under th is Act 8 ***.`
  line `18. Power of direct discount. — 9 *** When, in the opinion of the 10 [Bank] 11 ***, a special occasion`
  line `has arisen making it necessary or expedient that action should be taken 12 [under this section] for the`
  line `purposes of regulating credit in the interests of Indian 13 *** trade, commerce, industry and agricultural,`
  line `the Bank may, notwithstanding any limitation contained in 14 *** section 17, —`
  line `15 [( 1 ) purchase, sell or discount any bill of exchange or promissory note though such bill or`
  line `promissory note is not eligible for purchase or discount by the Bank under that section; or]`
  line `16 * * * * *`
  line `17 [( 3 ) make loans or advances to —`
  line `( a ) a State co - operative bank, or`
  line `( b ) on the recommendation of a State co - operative bank, to a cooperative society registered`
  line `within the area in which the State cooperative bank operates, or`
  line `( c ) any other person,`
  line `repayable on demand or on the expiry of the fixed periods, not exceeding ninety days, on such terms`
  line `and conditions as the Bank may consider to be sufficient.]`
  line `18 * * * * *`
  line `19 * * * * *`
  line `1. The words “and Burma” omitted by Act 11 of 1947, s. 11 (w.e.f. 1 - 4 - 1947).`
  line `2. Subs. by Act 32 of 1951, s. 7, for “share capital” (w.e.f. 1 - 11 - 1951).`
  line `3. Clause ( 14A ) omitted by Act 38 of 1959, s. 64 and the Third Schedule (w.e.f. 1 - 10 - 1959) which was inserted by Act 79 of`
  line `1956, s. 43 and the Second Schedule (w.e.f. 22 - 10 - 1956).`
  line `4. The words “and the making and issue of Burma notes in accordance with the law of Burma” omitted by Act 11 of 1947, s. 11`
  line `(w.e.f. 1 - 4 - 1947) which was inserted by the M.O. 1937.`
  line `5. The word “and” omitted by Ordinance 47 of 1945, s. 6.`
  line `6. Subs. by Act 23 of 1955, s. 52 and the Third Schedule for clause ( 15A ) (w.e.f. 1 - 7 - 1955).`
  line `7. Ins. by Act 58 of 1968, s. 24 (w.e.f. 1 - 2 - 1969).`
  line `8. The words “and the law of Burma” omitted by Act 11 of 1947, s. 11 (w.e.f. 1 - 4 - 1947) which was inserted by the M.O. 1937.`
  line `9. The brackets and figures “( 1 )” omitted by Act 51 of 1974, s. 7 (w.e.f. 13 - 12 - 1974).`
  line `10. Subs. by Act 32 of 1951, s. 8, for “Central Board” (w.e.f. 1 - 11 - 1951).`
  line `11. Certain words omitted by Act 62 of 1948, s. 7 and the Schedule (w.e.f. 1 - 1 - 1949).`
  line `12. Subs. by Act 51 of 1974, s. 7, for “under this sub - section” (w.e.f. 13 - 12 - 1974).`
  line `13. The words “or Burman” omitted by Act 11 of 1947, s. 12 (w.e.f. 1 - 4 - 1947) which was inserted by the M.O. 1937.`
  line `14. The words, brackets, letters and figures “sub - clauses ( a ) and ( b ) of clause ( 2 ) or sub - clause ( a ) or ( b ) of clause ( 3 ) or clause`
  line `( 4 ) of” omitted by Act 51 of 1974, s. 7 (w.e.f. 13 - 12 - 1974).`
  line `15. Subs. by s. 7, ibid., for clause ( 1 ) (w.e.f. 13 - 12 - 1974).`
  line `16. Clause ( 2 ) omitted by Act 24 of 1978, s. 5 (w.e.f. 21 - 7 - 1978).`
  line `17. Subs. by Act 51 of 1974, s. 7, for clause ( 3 ) (w.e.f. 13 - 12 - 1974).`
  line `18. The proviso omitted by Act 62 of 1948, s. 7 and the Schedule (w.e.f. 1 - 1 - 1949).`
  line `19. Sub - section ( 2 ) omitted by Act 51 of 1974, s. 7 (w.e.f. 13 - 12 - 1974).`
