obj_root_law_sections_30_content:
  string
  line 30
  line `be less than 1 [such per cent. of the total of the demand and ti me liabilities in India of such bank as shown`
  line `in the return referred to in sub - section ( 2 ), as the Bank may from time to time, having regard to the needs`
  line `of securing the monetary stability in the country, notify in the Gazette of India]:`
  line `2 * * * * *`
  line `Explanation. — For the purposes of this section, —`
  line `( a ) “ average daily balance ” shall mean the average of the balances held at the close of business of`
  line `each day 3 [of a fortnight];`
  line `4 [( b ) “ fortnight ” shall mean the period from Saturday to the second following Fr iday, both days`
  line inclusive;]
  line `5 [( c ) “ liabilities ” shall not include —`
  line `( i ) the paid - up capital or the reserves or any credit balance in the profit and loss account of`
  line `the bank;`
  line `( ii ) the amount of any loan taken from the Bank 6 *** 7 [or from the Exim Bank] 8 [or from the`
  line `Reconstruction Bank] 9 [or from the National Housing Bank ] or from the 10 [National Bank] 11 [or`
  line `f rom the Small Industries Bank 12 [ or from the National Bank for Financing Infrastructure and`
  line `Development or from the other development financial institution ] ] 13 ***;`
  line `( iii ) in the case of a State co - operative bank, also any loan taken by such bank from a State`
  line `Government 14 [or from the National Co - operative Development Corporation established under`
  line `the National Co - operative Development Corporation Act, 1962 (26 of 1962)] and any deposit of`
  line `money with such bank representing the reserve fund or any part thereof 15 *** maintained with it`
  line `by any co - operative society within its area of operation; ]`
  line `16 [ ( iv ) in the case of a State co - operative bank, which has granted an adv ance against any`
  line `balance maintained with it, such balance to the extent of the amount outstanding in respect of`
  line `such advance;]`
  line `1 3 [( v ) in the case a Regional Rural Bank, also any loan taken by su ch bank from its Sponsor`
  line Bank;]
  line `15 [( d ) the aggregate of the “ l iabilities ” of a Scheduled bank which is not a State co - operative`
  line `bank, to, —`
  line `( i ) the State Bank;`
  line `( ii ) a subsidiary bank as defined in section 2 of the State Bank of India (Subsidiary Banks)`
  line `Act, 1959 (38 of 1959);`
  line `( iii ) a corresponding new bank constituted by section 3 of the Banking Companies`
  line `(Acquisition and Transfer of Undertakings) Act, 1970 (5 of 1970);`
  line `1. Subs. by Act 26 of 2006, s. 3, for “three per cent. of the total of the demand and time liabilities in India of such bank as shown`
  line `in the return referred to in sub - section (2)” (w.e.f. 1 - 4 - 2007).`
  line `2. The proviso omitted by s. 3, ibid. (w.e.f. 1 - 4 - 2007).`
  line `3. Subs. by Act 1 of 1984, s. 6, for “of a week” (w.e.f. 29 - 3 - 1985).`
  line `4. Subs. by s. 6, ibid. for clause ( b ) (w.e.f. 29 - 3 - 1985).`
  line `5. Subs. by Act 23 of 1965, s. 6, for clause ( c ) (w.e.f. 1 - 3 - 1966).`
  line `6. The words “or f rom the Development Bank” omitted by Act 53 of 2003, s. 12 and the Schedule (w.e.f. 2 - 7 - 2004).`
  line `7. Ins. by Act 28 of 1981, s. 40 and the Second Schedule (w.e.f. 1 - 1 - 1982).`
  line `8. Ins. by Act 62 of 1984, s. 71 and the Third Schedule (w.e.f. 20 - 3 - 1985).`
  line `9. Ins. by Act 53 of 1987, s. 56 and the Second Schedule (w.e.f. 9 - 7 - 1988).`
  line `10. Subs. by Act 61 of 1981, s. 61 and the Second Schedule, for “Agricultural Refinance and Development Corporation”`
  line `(w.e.f. 12 - 7 - 1982).`
  line `11. Ins. by Act 39 of 1989, s. 53 and the Second Schedule (w.e.f. 7 - 3 - 1990).`
  line `12. Ins. by Act 17 of 2021, s. 47 and the S econd S chedule (w.e.f. 19 - 4 - 2021).`
  line `1 3. The words “or from the State Bank or from any other bank notified by the Central Government in this behalf, and” omitted by`
  line `Act 51 of 1974, s. 11 (w.e.f. 13 - 12 - 1974).`
  line `1 4. Ins. by Act 1 of 1984, s. 6 (w.e.f. 29 - 3 - 1985).`
  line `1 5. The words “required to be” omitted by Act 51 of 1974, s. 11 (w.e.f. 13 - 12 - 1974).`
  line `1 6. Ins. by s. 11, ibid. (w.e.f. 13 - 12 - 1974).`
