obj_root_law_sections_31_content:
  string
  line 31
  line `1 [( iiia ) a corresponding new bank constituted by section 3 of the Banking Companies`
  line `(Acquisition and Transfer of Undertakings) Act, 1980 (40 of 1980); ]`
  line `( iv ) a banking company as defined in clause ( c ) section 5 of the Banking Regulation Act,`
  line `1949 (10 of 1949);`
  line `( v ) a co - operative bank; or`
  line `( vi ) any other financial institution notified by the Central Government in this behalf,`
  line `shall be reduced by the aggrega te of the liabilities of all such banks and institutions to the scheduled bank;`
  line `( e ) the aggregate of the “ liabilities ” of a scheduled bank which is a State co - operative bank, to, —`
  line `( i ) the State Bank;`
  line `( ii ) a subsidiary bank as defined in section 2 of the State Bank of India (Subsidiary Banks)`
  line `Act, 1959 (38 of 1959);`
  line `( iii ) a corresponding new bank constituted by section 3 of the Banking Companies`
  line `(Acquisition and Transfer of Undertakings) Act, 1970 (5 of 1970);`
  line `1 [( iiia ) a corresponding new bank constituted by section 3 of the Banking Companies`
  line `(Acquisition and Transfer of Undertakings) Act, 1980 (40 of 1980);]`
  line `( iv ) a banking company as defined in clause ( c ) of section 5 of the Banking Regulation Act,`
  line `1949 (10 of 1949); or`
  line `( v ) any other financial institution notified by the Central Government in, this behalf,`
  line `shall be reduced by the aggregate of the liabilities of all such banks and institutions to the State co -`
  line `operative bank.]`
  line `( 1A ) Notwithstanding anything contained in sub - section ( 1 ), the Bank may, by notifi cation in the`
  line `Gazette of India, direct that every scheduled bank shall, with effect from such date as may be specified in`
  line `the notification, maintain with the Bank, in addition to the balance prescribed by or under sub - section ( 1 ),`
  line `an additional average dai ly balance the amount of which shall not be less than the 2 [rate specified in the`
  line `notification, such additional balance being calculated with reference to the excess of the total of the`
  line `demand and time liabilities of the bank as shown in the return referre d to in sub - section ( 2 ) over the total`
  line `of its demand and time liabilities] at the close of business on the date specified in the notification as`
  line `shown by such return so however, that the additional balance shall, in no case, be more than such excess:`
  line `3 [Pro vided that the Bank may, by a separate notification in the Gazette of India, specify different`
  line `dates in respect of a Bank subsequently included in the Second Schedule].`
  line `4 * * * * *`
  line `1 [ 1C ) The Bank may, for the purposes of this section, specify from t ime to time with reference to any`
  line `transaction or class of transactions that such transaction or transactions shall be regarded as liability in`
  line `India of a scheduled bank, and if any question arises as to whether any transaction or class of transactions`
  line `shal l be regarded, for the purposes of this section, as liability in India of a scheduled bank, the decision of`
  line `the Bank thereon shall be final.]`
  line `5 [( 2 ) Every scheduled bank shall send to the Bank a return signed by two responsible officers of such`
  line `bank showing —`
  line `( a ) the amount of its demand and time liabilities and the amount of its borrowings from banks in`
  line `India, 6 [classifying them into demand and time liabilities],`
  line `1. Ins. by Act 1 of 1984, s. 6 (w.e.f. 29 - 3 - 1985).`
  line `2. Subs. by Act 35 of 1962, s. 3, for certain words (w.e.f. 15 - 9 - 1962).`
  line `3. Added by Act 1 of 1984, s. 6 (w.e.f. 29 - 3 - 1985).`
  line `4. Sub - sections ( 1AA ) and ( 1B ) omitted by Act 26 of 2006, s. 3 (w.e.f. 1 - 4 - 2007).`
  line `5. Subs. by Act 32 of 1951, s. 16, for sub - section ( 2 ) (w.e.f. 1 - 11 - 1951).`
  line `6. Subs. by Act 51 of 1974, s. 11, for “other than the State Bank and any other bank notified by the Central Government in th is`
  line `behalf” (w.e.f. 13 - 12 - 1974).`
