obj_root_law_sections_37_content:
  string
  line 37
  line `Provided that any credit information received by a banking company under this clause shall not`
  line `be published except in ac cordance with the practice and usage customary among bankers or as`
  line `permitted or required under any other law.]`
  line `( 3 ) Notwithstanding anything contained in any law for the time being in force, no court, tribunal or`
  line `other authority shall compel the Bank or any banking company to produce or to give inspection of any`
  line `statement submitted by that banking company under section 45C or to disclose any credit information`
  line `furnished by the Bank to that banking company under section 45 D.`
  line `45F. Certain claims for compensat ion barred. — No person shall have any right, whether in`
  line `contract or otherwise, to any compensation for any loss incurred by reason of the operation of any of the`
  line `provisions of this Chapter.`
  line `45G. [ Penalties ]. — Omitted by the Reserve Bank of India ( Amendment ) Act, 1974 (51 of l974), s. 15`
  line `( w.e.f. 13 - 12 - 1974). ]`
  line `1 [ CHAPTER IIIB`
  line `P ROVISIONS RELATING TO NON - BANKING INSTITUTIONS RECEIVING DEPOSITS AND`
  line FINANCIALINSTITUTIONS
  line `45H. Chapter IIIB not to apply in certain cases. — The provisions of this Chapter shall not apply to`
  line `the State Bank or a banking company as defined in section 5 of the 2 [Banking Regulation Act, 1949 (10 of`
  line `1949) ] or 3 [a corresponding new bank as defined in clause ( da ) of section 5 of th at Act or a subsidiary`
  line `bank as defined in the State Bank of India (Subsidiary Banks) Act, 1959 (38 of 1959)] or 4 [a Regional`
  line `Rural Bank or a co - operative bank ] or a primary agricultural credit society or a primary credit society]:`
  line `Provided that for the purposes of this Chapter, the 5 [Tamil Nadu Indust rial Investment`
  line `Corporation Limited] shall not be deemed to be a banking company.`
  line `45 - I. Definitions. — In this Chapter, unless the context otherwise requires, —`
  line `6 [( a ) “ business of a non - banking financial institution ” means carrying on the business of a`
  line `financial institution referred to in clause ( c ) and includes business of a non - banking financial`
  line `company referred to in clause ( f );]`
  line `7 [( aa )] “ company ” means a company as defined in section 3 of the Companies Act, 1956 ( 1 of`
  line `1956), and includes a foreign company within the meaning of section 591 of that Act;`
  line `( b ) “ corporation ” means a corporation incorporated by an Act of any legislature;`
  line `8 [( bb ) “ deposit ” includes and shall be deemed always to have include any receipt of m oney by`
  line `way of deposit or loan or in any ot her form, but does not include, —`
  line `( i ) amounts raised by way of share capital;`
  line `( ii ) amounts contributed as capital by partners of a firm;`
  line `( iii ) amounts received from a scheduled bank or a co - operative bank or any other banking`
  line `company as defined in clause ( c ) of section 5 of a Banking Regulation Act, 1949 (10 of 1949);`
  line `( iv ) any amount received from, —`
  line `9 * * * * *`
  line `( b ) a State Financial Corporation,`
  line `1. Ins. by Act 55 of 1963, s. 5 (w.e.f. 1 - 2 - 1964).`
  line `2. Subs. b y Act 51 of 1974, s. 3, for “Banking Companies Act, 1949” (w.e.f. 13 - 12 - 1974).`
  line `3. Subs. by Act 1 of 1984, s. 8, for “a banking institution notified under section 51 of that Act” (w.e.f. 15 - 2 - 1984).`
  line `4. Subs. by Act 21 of 1976, s. 33, for “a co - operative ban k” (w.e.f. 26 - 9 - 1975).`
  line `5. Subs. by Act 51 of 1974, s. 16, for “Madras Industrial Investment Corporation Limited” (w.e.f. 13 - 12 - 1974).`
  line `6. Ins. by Act 23 of 1997, s. 2 (w.e.f. 9 - 1 - 1997).`
  line `7. Clause ( a ) renumbered as clause ( aa ) thereof by s. 2, ibid. (w.e.f. 9 - 1 - 1997).`
  line `8. Subs. by Act 1 of 1984, s. 9, for clause ( bb ) (w.e.f. 15 - 2 - 1984).`
  line `9. Item ( a ) omitted by Act 53 of 2003, s. 12 and the Schedule (w.e.f. 2 - 7 - 2004).`
