obj_root_law_sections_63_content:
  string
  line 63
  line `( 2 ) If any person fails to produce any book, account or other document or to furnish any statement,`
  line `information or particulars which, under this Act or any order, regulation or direction made or given`
  line `thereunder, it is his duty to produce or furnish or to an swer any question put to him in pursuance of the`
  line `provisions of this Act or of any order, regulation or direction made or given thereunder, he shall be`
  line `punishable with fine which may extend to 1 [one lakh rupees] in respect of each offence and if he persists`
  line `in such failure or refusal, with further fine which may extend to 2 [five thousand rupees] for every day,`
  line `after the first during which the offence continues.`
  line `( 3 ) If any person contravenes the provisions of section 31, he shall be punishable with fine which may`
  line `extend to the amount of the bill of exchange, hundi, promissory note or engagement for payment of`
  line `money in respect whereof the offence is committed.`
  line `( 4 ) If any person discloses any credit information, the disclosure of which is prohibited under sectio n`
  line `45E, he shall be punishable with imprisonment for a term which may extend to six mounts, or with fine`
  line `which may extend to one thousand rupees, or with both.`
  line `3 [( 4A ) If any person contravenes the provisions of sub - section ( 1 ) of section 45 - IA, he shall be`
  line `punishable with imprisonment for a term which shall not be less than one year but which may extend to`
  line `five years and with fine which shall not be less than one lakh rupees but which may extend to 4 [twenty -`
  line `five lakh rupees].`
  line `( 4AA ) If any auditor fails to comply with any direction given or order made by the Bank under`
  line `section 45MA, he shall be punishable with fine which may extend to 5 [ten lakh rupees].`
  line `( 4AAA ) Whoever fails to comply with any order made by the Company Law Board under`
  line `sub - section ( 2 ) of section 45QA, shall be punishable with imprisonment for a term which may extend to`
  line `three years and shall also be liable to a fine of not less than 6 [ five thousand rupees] for every day during`
  line `which such non - compliance continues.]`
  line `( 5 ) If any person 7 [other than an au ditor] —`
  line `( a ) receives 8 [any deposit without being authorised so to do or] in contravention of any direction`
  line `given or order made under Chapter IIIB; or`
  line `1 [( aa ) fails to comply with any direction given or order made by the Bank under any of the`
  line `provisions of Chapter IIIB; or]`
  line `( b ) issues any prospectus or advertisement otherwise than in accordance with 9 [ section 45 J] or`
  line `any order made under section 45], as the case may be,`
  line `he shall be punishable with imprisonment for a term which may extend to three years and shall also be`
  line `l iable to fine which may extend, —`
  line `( i ) in the case of a contravention falling under clause ( a ), to twice the amount of the deposit`
  line `received; and`
  line `( ii ) in the case of a contravention falling under clause ( b ), to twice the amount of the deposit`
  line `called for by the prospectus or advertisement.`
  line `10 [( 5A ) If any person contravenes any provision of section 45S, he shall be punishable with`
  line `imprisonment for a term which may extend to two years, or with fine which may extend to twice the`
  line `1. Subs. by Act 23 of 2019, s. 142, for “two thousand rupees” (w.e.f. 9 - 8 - 2019).`
  line `2. Subs. by s. 142, ibid., for “one hundred rupees” (w.e.f. 9 - 8 - 2019).`
  line `3. Ins. by Act 23 of 1997, s. 10 (w.e.f. 9 - 1 - 1997).`
  line `4. Subs. by Act 23 of 2019, s. 142, for “five lakh rupees” (w.e.f. 9 - 8 - 2019).`
  line `5. Subs. by s. 142, ibid., for “ five thousand rupee” (w.e.f. 9 - 8 - 2019).`
  line `6. Subs. by s. 142, ibid., for “ rupees fifty” (w.e.f. 9 - 8 - 2019).`
  line `7. Ins. by Act 23 of 1997, s. 10 (w.e.f. 9 - 1 - 1997).`
  line `8. Subs. by Act 23 of 2019, s. 142, for “any deposit” (w.e.f. 9 - 8 - 2019).`
  line `9. Subs. by s. 142, ibid., for the “section 45NA” (w.e.f. 9 - 8 - 2019).`
  line `10. Ins. by Act 1 of 1984, s. 11 (w.e.f. 15 - 2 - 1984 ).`
