  line `1 [THE FIRST SCHEDULE`
  line `[ See section 9]`
  line `2 [1. The Western Area shall consist of the States of Goa, Gujarat, Madhya Pradesh and`
  line `Maharashtra and the Union t erritories of Dadra and Nagar Haveli, and Daman and Diu.`
  line `2. The Eastern Area shall consist of the States of Arunachal Pradesh, Assam, Bihar, Manipur,`
  line `Meghalaya, Mizoram, Nagaland, Orissa, Sikkim, Tripura and West Bengal and the Union`
  line `territories of Andaman and Nicobar Islands.]`
  line `3. The Northern Area shall consist of the States of Jammu and Kashmir, 3 [Punjab,`
  line `Harya na,] 4 [Himachal Pradesh], Rajasthan and Uttar Pradesh and the Union territories of`
  line `5 [Chandigarh] 6 [and Delhi].`
  line `4. The Southern area shall consist of the States of Andhra Pradesh, 7 [Karnataka], 8 [Tamil Nadu]`
  line `and Kerala and the 9 [Union territories of Pondicherry and 10 [Lakshadweep]].]`
  line `1. Subs. by the Adaptation of Laws (No. 3) Order, 1956, for the former First Schedule.`
  line `2. Subs. by Act 23 of 1997, s. 12, for items 1 and 2 (w.e.f. 9 - 1 - 1997).`
  line `3. Subs. by the Punjab Reorganisation and Delhi High Court (Adaptation of Laws on Union Subjects) Order, 1968, for “Punjab”`
  line `(w.e.f. 1 - 11 - 1956).`
  line `4. Ins. by the State of Himachal Pradesh (Adaptation of Laws on Union Subjects) Order, 1973 (w.e.f. 25 - 1 - 1971).`
  line `5. Ins. by the Punjab Reorganisation and Delhi High Court (Adaptation of Laws on Union Subjects) Order, 1968 (w.e.f. 1 - 11 -`
  line `1966).`
  line `6. Subs. by the State of Himachal Pradesh (Adaptation of Laws on Union Subjects) Order, 1973, for “Himachal Pradesh and`
  line `Delhi” (w.e.f. 25 - 1 - 1971).`
  line `7. Subs. by the Mysore State (Alteration of Name) (Adaptation of Laws on Union Subjects) Order, 1974, for “Mysor e”`
  line `(w.e.f. 1 - 11 - 1973).`
  line `8. Subs. by the Madras State (Alteration of Name) Adaptation of Laws on Union Subjects) Order, 1970, for “Madras”`
  line `(w.e.f. 14 - 1 - 1969).`
  line `9. Subs. by Reg. 7 of 1963, s. 8, for “Union territory of La ccadive, Minicoy and Admindivi Islands”.`
  line `10. Subs. by the Laccadive, Minicoy and Amindivi Islands (Alteration of Name) Adaptation of Laws Order, 1974, for`
  line `“Laccadive, Minicoy and Amindivi Islands.” (w.e.f. 1 - 11 - 1973).`
